/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: "SYS_RoleMenu" */
/*==============================================================*/
create table "SYS_RoleMenu"
(
"RoleMenuID" NUMBER(10) not null,
"RoleID" NUMBER(10) not null,
"MenuID" NUMBER(10) not null,
"Enable" INTEGER default 1 not null,
"CreateBy" NUMBER(32) not null,
"CreateTime" TIMESTAMP default SYSDATE not null,
constraint PK_SYS_ROLEMENU primary key ("RoleMenuID")
);

comment on column "SYS_RoleMenu"."Enable" is
'1：启用
0：停用';

alter table "SYS_RoleMenu"

references "SYS_Menu" ("MenuID");

alter table "SYS_RoleMenu"
add constraint FK_SYS_ROLEMENU_2_SYS_ROLE_PK foreign key ("RoleID")
references "SYS_Role" ("RoleID");
